  "instructions": [
    "Slice the avocado and scoop out its flesh into a mixing bowl.",
    "Core and chop the tomato finely, then add it to the bowl with the avocado.",
    "Add the juice of one lime to both ingredients for acidity.",
    "Fold in chopped cilantro leaves. Use your hands if you’re comfortable with cilantro, or use tongs.",
    "Drizzle a few drops of ghee over the salad and gently stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve immediately as a light snack."
